      { "text": "6x + 1", "isCorrect": false },
      { "text": "3x² - 2", "isCorrect": false }
    ],
    "explanation": "Using power rule: d/dx(3x²) = 6x, d/dx(-2x) = -2, d/dx(1) = 0. So f'(x) = 6x - 2.",
    "points": 3,
